  "texts": [
    "Our case study findings also show that the respondents experience ChatGPT as beneficial and demonstrate that they would benefit more if it is integrated with the organizational knowledge base.",
    "Therefore, this study helps policymakers to generate synergies through the symbiosis of human and emerging technology in organizations at a fast pace.",
    "We underline that our proposed conceptualization is subject to further investigations, especially the deployment of ChatGPT mediated knowledge management systems in organizations;",
    "moreover, researchers and practitioners should exercise caution in the adoption of artificial intelligence or ChatGPT, as these fields are evolving and, therefore, new challenges and opportunities are emerging (Burger et al., 2023).",
